Phase Auto Updater\par
\par
This installer adds the Phase Auto Updater for the current Windows user. It creates normal Windows shortcuts and can start the updater when you sign in.\par
\par
The updater is for installing and keeping the Phase Animator Roblox Studio plugin current on this computer.\par
\par
By continuing, you agree to install Phase Auto Updater on this device.\par
